---

<section id="faq" class="mx-auto max-w-2xl py-24 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-heading text-center mb-16 uppercase">
        QUESTIONS? <span class="italic underline">ANSWERS.</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
        <details
            class="group rounded-base border-2 border-border bg-white p-6 shadow-shadow open:bg-main transition-colors"
        >
            <summary
                class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-xl uppercase"
            >
                Is it really 0% commission?
                <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-3xl"
                    >+</span
                >
            </summary>
            <div class="mt-4 font-bold text-lg">
                Yes. We charge a fixed monthly fee. Whether you do 100 or 10,000
                orders, you never pay us a percentage.
            </div>
        </details>
        <details
            class="group rounded-base border-2 border-border bg-white p-6 shadow-shadow open:bg-main transition-colors"
        >
            <summary
                class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-xl uppercase"
            >
                Do I get a mobile app?
                <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-3xl"
                    >+</span
                >
            </summary>
            <div class="mt-4 font-bold text-lg">
                You get a progressive web app (PWA) that works perfectly on all
                devices, plus native iOS/Android options for enterprise plans.
            </div>
        </details>
        <details
            class="group rounded-base border-2 border-border bg-white p-6 shadow-shadow open:bg-main transition-colors"
        >
            <summary
                class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-xl uppercase"
            >
                How long does setup take?
                <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-45 text-3xl"
                    >+</span
                >
            </summary>
            <div class="mt-4 font-bold text-lg">
                Usually less than 24 hours. We help you upload your menu and
                configure your delivery zones so you can start selling
                immediately.
            </div>
        </details>
    </div>
</section>
